## 2. Relationships & Entity Graph

As visualized via `/graphify`, the fee system revolves around the `FeeStructure` and `StudentEnrollment`.

```mermaid
graph TD
    School --> FeeHead
    School --> FeeStructure
    AcademicYear --> FeeStructure
    
    FeeStructure --> FeeStructureItem
    FeeHead --> FeeStructureItem
    
    FeeStructure --> FeeInstallment
    
    StudentEnrollment --> FeeAssignment
    FeeStructure --> FeeAssignment
    
    StudentEnrollment --> LedgerEntry
    LedgerEntry --> Payment
```

